[DTO] UserRecordDto: email, passwordHash, teamId, roleId, role, level
    stored user identity with role fields
[DTO] CreateTeamDto: name, slug, parentId, leaderId
    input for creating a new team
[DTO] UpdateTeamDto: teamId, name?, slug?, leaderId?
    input for updating team fields
[DTO] TeamDto: teamId, name, slug, parentId, leaderId
    stored team entity with member list
[DTO] AddMemberDto: teamId, memberEmail
    input for adding a team member
[DTO] RemoveMemberDto: teamId, memberEmail
    input for removing a team member
[DTO] ChangeLeaderDto: teamId, leaderId
    input for changing a team leader
[DTO] CreateRoleDto: name, level
    input for creating a role definition
[DTO] UpdateRoleDto: roleId, name?, level?
    input for updating role fields
[DTO] RoleDefDto: roleId, name, level
    stored role definition entity
[DTO] CreateUserDto: email, password, teamId, roleId
    input for creating a new user
[DTO] DeactivateUserDto: email
    input for soft-deleting a user
[DTO] ChangePasswordDto: email, password, newPassword
    input for changing a user password
[DTO] SuccessDto: result
